{
  "stem": "1061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a selection when my sis-- my older sister, Anna, the one from Canada, she was really hallucinating.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she was saying things, and she was-- she was burning up with fever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to prop her up and stand her up for the-- for the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whatever it was-- exam.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a selection, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came to see what was cooking, and this out, this out, this out, this out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember now distinctly that, because I worked in the laundry when I had typhus, and that was one of these-- these line ups again, the women I worked with in the laundry told me to come in and they put me over a steaming cauldron.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I was so burning up with fever, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must have looked like a ghost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that saved me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These women in the laundry saved me, because the steam was over me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And besides, they just looked in and they saw everybody working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't-- they didn't bother to come in and see what's what, because everybody was busy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As far as I remember, if there was anything-- I mean, if you cut-- if anything happened to you-- you cut your hand and you had to bleed and that was the hand you worked with-- maybe they allowed you to have to go and have a kind of a bandage with a little iodine.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because after all, you know, you couldn't go to work next day if you-- you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But basically, whoever was sick or in any way unfit for heavy labor just was-- was totally dismissed as a human being, as a person, as anything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't count anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
